summary: 2018.11 Group Order Leftovers Here are all the spare goods leftover from the 2018.11 Group Order! If you’re a GO participant and...
caption:
2018.11 Group Order Leftovers

Here are all the spare goods leftover from the 2018.11 Group Order!

If you’re a GO participant and would like to add something to your existing order, please let me know asap. I’ll invoice you for the additional items before I seal up your package for shipping later this week. 

  1. HQ items - £4 each
  2. BNHA items - unless specified with a price, everything else is £4
  3. BNHA badges (5cm wide) - £4 each
  4. Misc items - £4 each (please note that the acrylic Ryunosuke with bouquet doesn’t have a base, that’s why is cheaper) 
  5. Todoroki x Midoriya x Eri fan designed acrylic stand - £12 (btw they changed the design and the new batch has a rectangular base)
  6. BNHA / Cardcaptor Sakura / Houseki no Kuni fan designed postcard sets (visit the website or check tags for previews) - £10 each

Other than these new additions, more spare goods are listed on hachisales.com in the Buy Now section.

summary:
Yaoyorozu: "Knowledge" is knowing that a tomato is a fruit; "wisdom" is not putting it in a fruit salad.
Sero: That was...
body:
Yaoyorozu: "Knowledge" is knowing that a tomato is a fruit; "wisdom" is not putting it in a fruit salad.
Sero: That was deep.
Midoriya: "Philosophy" is wondering if that means ketchup is a smoothie.
Todoroki: That was deeper.
Kaminari: "Common sense" is knowing that ketchup isn't a damn smoothie, you nasties.
